{"id":600068,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【立此存照】又有品牌辱华了-注意要开始抵制了/","date":"2018-11-21T11:25:51Z","modified":"2018-11-21T11:27:44Z","title":"【立此存照】又有品牌辱华了 注意要开始抵制了","content":"<p>近日，意大利品牌Dolce &amp; Gabbana定于11月21日在上海博览中心举办首个大型时装秀“The Great Show”。为此，Dolce &amp;Gabbana特别拍摄了一个把中国传统与意大利经典饮食相结合的广告宣传片，标题为“起筷吃饭”。</p>\n<p>然而有部分中国网友认为该片内容涉嫌歧视，要求设计师Stefano Gabbana对此做出道歉。</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KvSVYphuDYo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>之后，在一些网友po出的非完整的与设计师私人聊天内容截图中，Stefano Gabbana本人使用了“all the worlwide know your attitude for ecxemple with dogs”，“the country of shit is china”等语句，则被进一步被认定为“辱华言论”，引发后续抗议。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/229R-hnyuqhi6253801.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600071\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/229R-hnyuqhi6253801.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"791\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/229R-hnyuqhi6253801.jpg 1242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/229R-hnyuqhi6253801-171x300.jpg 171w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/229R-hnyuqhi6253801-768x1350.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/229R-hnyuqhi6253801-582x1024.jpg 582w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Hn8r-hmhhnqt2766420.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600072\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Hn8r-hmhhnqt2766420.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Hn8r-hmhhnqt2766420.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Hn8r-hmhhnqt2766420-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Hn8r-hmhhnqt2766420-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/HuyO-hmivixn5759033.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600073\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/HuyO-hmivixn5759033.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/HuyO-hmivixn5759033.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/HuyO-hmivixn5759033-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/HuyO-hmivixn5759033-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/IISU-hmivixn5748851.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600074\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/IISU-hmivixn5748851.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/IISU-hmivixn5748851.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/IISU-hmivixn5748851-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/IISU-hmivixn5748851-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>该“辱华事件”在墙内新浪微博进行广泛传播报道后，共青团中央、人民日报等最终予以了定性：自取其辱。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600078\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"466\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态2.jpg 848w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态2-300x254.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态2-768x651.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_600075\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/翻译.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-600075\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/翻译.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"259\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/翻译.jpg 1013w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/翻译-300x155.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/翻译-768x397.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">国内媒体报道的蜜汁翻译</p></div>\n<blockquote><p>@共青团中央 ：我们欢迎外国企业来华投资兴业，同时在华经营的外国企业也应当尊重中国，尊重中国人民。这也是任何企业到其他国家投资兴业、开展合作最起码的遵循。@DolceGabbana ​​​​</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/61add7e3ly1fxfpkz0mjqj20om0f7q4n.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-600076 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/61add7e3ly1fxfpkz0mjqj20om0f7q4n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/61add7e3ly1fxfpkz0mjqj20om0f7q4n.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/61add7e3ly1fxfpkz0mjqj20om0f7q4n-300x185.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/61add7e3ly1fxfpkz0mjqj20om0f7q4n-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"mceTemp\"></div>\n<p>DolceGabbana ​​​对此事件的的解释是，官方Intragram账号和Stefano Gabbana的Intragram账号被盗，并对此道歉，但显然这种中国式的公关手法并不能使得中国网友买账。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-600069 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg.jpg 733w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg-300x194.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600070\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg2.jpg 743w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg2-300x177.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/dg2-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>该事件升温过程中，中国艺人们继续接力，原计划参与时装秀的相关艺人宣布罢演，包括：迪丽热巴、陈坤、东方宾利、王大陆、木子洋、李冰冰、胡兵、王俊凯等，甚至还有“火速解约”举动。</p>\n<blockquote><p>相关阅读：<span id=\".E3.80.90.E5.BC.82.E9.97.BB.E8.A7.82.E6.AD.A2.E3.80.91.E5.BD.B1.E6.98.9F.E6.8E.A5.E5.8A.9B.E2.80.9C.E4.B8.AD.E5.9B.BD.EF.BC.8C.E4.B8.80.E7.82.B9.E4.B8.8D.E8.83.BD.E5.B0.91.E2.80.9D\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/%E3%80%90%E5%BC%82%E9%97%BB%E8%A7%82%E6%AD%A2%E3%80%91%E5%BD%B1%E6%98%9F%E6%8E%A5%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%91/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">【异闻观止】影星接力“中国，一点不能少”</a></span></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/006Qht3Ely1fxftnske4wj31wy2pitzm-e1542798248762.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600080\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/006Qht3Ely1fxftnske4wj31wy2pitzm-e1542798248762.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/006Qht3Ely1fxftnske4wj31wy2pitzm-e1542798248762.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/006Qht3Ely1fxftnske4wj31wy2pitzm-e1542798248762-300x287.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/006Qht3Ely1fxftnske4wj31wy2pitzm-e1542798248762-220x210.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>官方媒体对于艺人集体退出DG大型时装秀“The Great Show”持支持态度。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600079\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"805\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态3.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态3-205x300.jpg 205w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态3-700x1024.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有网友 @SerenaHottie 制作“反歧视视频”予以回击，声称：免费教他们怎么用刀叉吃中国美食，学会了再来办秀赚钱。</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3RbiLzE6rL0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>该事件目前已被 @思想火炬 官方账号列为 #意识形态要闻。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600077\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"575\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态.jpg 745w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/意识形态-287x300.jpg 287w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E8%BE%B1%E5%8D%8E\">辱华</a></p>\n<p><span id=\".E3.80.90.E7.BD.91.E7.BB.9C.E6.B0.91.E8.AE.AE.E3.80.91.E6.97.A9.E8.AF.B4.E8.BF.87.E5.A2.99.E6.98.AF.E7.94.A8.E6.9D.A5.E4.BF.9D.E6.8A.A4.E5.A4.96.E5.9B.BD.E7.BD.91.E5.8F.8B.E7.9A.84\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/%E3%80%90%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%91%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%91%E6%97%A9%E8%AF%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%A2%99%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B%E7%9A%84/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">【网络民议】早说过墙是用来保护外国网友的</a></span></p>\n<p><a title=\"德国之声 | “是可忍孰不可忍” 中国上下反“辱华”\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/%e5%be%b7%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0-%e6%98%af%e5%8f%af%e5%bf%8d%e5%ad%b0%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af%e5%bf%